## Bugs

At the moment, the protocol mechanism is infected by Loopback echo. This phenomenon (that to be honest i didn't see anything on internet, this name comes from gemni pro) has the follow conseguences: When a sender sends his protocol package, and the follow step is listen the response, can happening that the sender re-takes his own message back as response from his destinator. This as you can immagine generate a big problem during the comunication.

